{
  "character_description": "The Hair Hanger is a suspended acrobatic fighter based on the supplied Stamptown reference photo: a performer hanging from a wrapped high bun attached to a metal ring, wearing a tied white shirt over a red performance top, red bottoms, visible tattoos, and bright yellow-orange striped socks. She never plants on the floor and fights by tucking, swinging, hairpin tossing, and spinning around the hair-hanging point.\nSilhouette: compact suspended acrobat, high wrapped bun and metal ring above the head, one knee often tucked.\nClothing: tied white shirt, red/pink performance top and bottoms, yellow-orange striped socks.\nAccessories: hair-hanging rig, wrapped bun tie, small metal hairpin projectile.\nDistinctive traits: tattoo flashes, stage grin, green stage-light spin trails.",
